{"tid":1584621,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"緊急 - 連登有問題？ 連仔入一入黎","createTime":"2019-09-21T08:25:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T08:46:51.000Z","uid":196227,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f75ebb78c05db9d8971d3ce3ee765197a76e7efb","tid":1584621,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T08:25:55.000Z","msg":"1）帳號保護功能冇晒<br />\n<br />\n大家都知連仔整咗好多保護功能<br />\n<br />\n可以Set開post、留言、個人資料功能等等，有密碼先入到<br />\n<br />\n但係呢幾日用用吓發覺，順手咗咁多？<br />\n原來係全部Set密碼功能冇晒，大家留意吓<br />\n<br />\n到底點解會咁？<br />\n係連仔你做咗野？<br />\n定同最近連登app要重新安裝有關？（比人hack咗？）<br />\n<br />\n而我係連登apps無法正常開啓前，連接apps途中，彈咗句「更新資料庫」。 我見到呢句都好懷疑有人hack緊我account。 有冇人同我一樣有相同情況？<br />\n<br />\n而我甚至草稿被全部刪除，啱啱開草稿冇晒我發送失敗/儲存草稿。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2）連登廣告重返？<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日我有時睇連登，發覺有番廣告，以為連仔頂唔住，要開番，覺得冇咩大問題，所以冇特登cap低。<br />\n<br />\n但係發現咗第一點之後，開始懷疑。<br />\n到底連仔你係唔係出咗咩事？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3） 熱門post不正常<br />\n<br />\n大量post得幾十個讚，都唔係好多人留言，突然之間上晒熱門。<br />\n而重點其他留言量高、讚人數多既好快沉底。<br />\n好似逼人留意嗰部份廢post咁<br />\n呢幾個星期行動post大家有眼睇，雖然推人數小咗，但係理應保持係熱門，結果好快沉晒。<br />\n<br />\n另外有部份post更被偷偷刪除<br />\n<br />\n4） 發生事故，連仔不再置頂回應？<br />\n<br />\n已往連登有咩問題，連仔都會出post/彈提示信息出黎，表明服務器有問題及解釋。<br />\n<br />\n但係最近連登apps不穩定，甚至大部份人要重裝apps先用到，連仔冇任何解釋？<br />\n<br />\n其次有大量post被刪除，已有大量巴絲開post討論，結果不了了知，被忽視。<br />\n<br />\n連仔你係唔係比人捉住咗？或者現在根本不受你操控？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連仔回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一點真係好嚴重<br />\n<br />\n絕無半點假話<br />\n歡迎起我底，五毛死全家<br />\n0<br />\n0"},{"pid":"8beabe7ba1def230084683642ccf37f85e770fb2","tid":1584621,"uid":196227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T08:26:37.000Z","msg":"各位有冇相同疑惑？"},{"pid":"a27956f516de17405a9dc292665d88f6a7a2337f","tid":1584621,"uid":1554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T08:26:50.000Z","msg":"omg 推"},{"pid":"d3f813260e917b0bd060e25738b569d3e6de06d9","tid":1584621,"uid":210672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T08:26:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c23c843c1745a83c24d4a4be1cbd25a795f3a4","tid":1584621,"uid":240344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T08:27:28.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"4cded74976691a219faffe852a27bb78e3d78c3b","tid":1584621,"uid":138361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T08:27:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6878f3800b0fd706b471722290d379d6e348560f","tid":1584621,"uid":1554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T08:27:48.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"a43689871f46ec9f82945b5a6c3a1adf0af0f2d0","tid":1584621,"uid":240344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T08:27:50.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"33f47aad2fcb2dab5f6ae86a40dfa426fd980914","tid":1584621,"uid":1554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T08:28:02.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"d53c95934fb1ad23f5f7f5d19c57791292938fc7","tid":1584621,"uid":240344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T08:28:03.000Z","msg":"連仔出左事？"},{"pid":"5fffc35879cdab498cca6c5ed034c2b2bd4631fe","tid":1584621,"uid":248670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T08:28:16.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"f1fbd8379b4b3f4079c64352f54eead9ce4e12d5","tid":1584621,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T08:29:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連仔"},{"pid":"5766f1dc64043b556b68a8b22dea87304e2a460d","tid":1584621,"uid":1554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T08:29:57.000Z","msg":"Test咗app內更改密碼、更改帳戶資料都係要重新登入"},{"pid":"e2d3fcb453399a5b4226e66d8d230622e365dca0","tid":1584621,"uid":285854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite